snippet.title: Project '06 -  Demo Release
snippet.description:
An insanely ambitious project carrying an incredibily huge effort between me and a few friends. Hope you enjoy!

The demo contains only Wave Ocean & Kingdom Valley.

Credit to BrianuuSonic & UltimateDarkman for the concept behind the cutscene in Kingdom Valley.

(UPDATED TO SILVER RELEASE PATCH V1.4)
Download:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1klUEs43gzyqgnsDT9tlTyxy0WYPzLGde/view?usp=sharing
Mirrors:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oXrQqYzPupzdbZaroTTdgm_uRanXvTAP/view?usp=sharing
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Pjq18ZTvgusqHpX0hpYiu_vad0ECJEvx/view?usp=sharing
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DgOhhbqNlY7wdsaHAG_A6DebNFycsvnM/view?usp=sharing
ANOTHER Mirror:
https://www.mediafire.com/file/spy9bu2ffzt0wwz/Project_06_-_Silver_Release_%2528Patch_v1.4%2529.zip/file

Editing and composition by ChaosX.
Footage recorded by BeatZ:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEjwges-3BTaWsMwOGJDoGQ
